net.opentsdb.query

类 QueryLimitOverride

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.query.QueryLimitOverride
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.jboss.netty.util.TimerTask

    public class QueryLimitOverride
extends Object
implements org.jboss.netty.util.TimerTask
    A class used for numeric query overrides using regular expression matching. The class will attempt to load from a locally cached file on construction if a file is given. Each time one or more items are added or removed to the list the file will be updated if it was configured. This class is thread safe.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.4

      • TR_OVERRIDES

        public static com.fasterxml.jackson.core.type.TypeReference<HashSet<QueryLimitOverride.QueryLimitOverrideItem>> TR_OVERRIDES
        Used for deserialization the proper object. Without this the hash codes /* won't function properly as Jackson may just create a hash map for our simple /* object.

    • 构造器详细资料

      • QueryLimitOverride

        public QueryLimitOverride(TSDB tsdb)
        Default ctor. If a file location is given, it will be read on construction and reloaded every interval seconds. Note that if there is a problem reading or parsing the config file (when set) the ctor will continue loading with the defaults and if an interval is set, will attempt to reload at a later time.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to which we belong.
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the default limits are less than zero.

      • getByteLimit

        public long getByteLimit(String metric)
        Iterates over the list of overrides and return the first that matches or the default if no match is found. NOTE: The set of expressions is not sorted so if more than one regex matches the string, the result is indeterministic. If the metric is null or empty, the default limit is returned.
        参数:
        metric - The string to match
        返回:
        The matched or default limit.

      • getDataPointLimit

        参数:

        返回:
        The matched or default limit.
